!!!
%html{:lang => "en"}
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}
    %meta{:charset => "UTF-8"}
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=5.0,minimum-scale=1.0,shrink-to-fit=no", :name => "viewport"}
    %meta{:content => "ie=edge", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}
    %meta{:content => "no-cache", "http-equiv" => "pragma"}
    %meta{:content => "index,follow", :name => "robots"}
    %title Hourglass
    %meta{:content => "Tabler comes with tons of well-designed components and features. Start your adventure with Tabler and make your dashboard great again. For free!", :name => "description"}

  %body
    .page
      %header.header.js-header
        .container
          .d-flex.align-items-center.position-relative
            %a.logo{:href => "/"}
              %img{:alt => "Tabler UI Kit", :src => "/img/tabler.svg", :title => ""}/
              %div
                Hourglass
            %a.header-menu-btn
              %svg.feather.feather-menu{:fill => "none", :height => "24", :stroke => "currentColor", "stroke-linecap" => "round", "stroke-linejoin" => "round", "stroke-width" => "2", :viewbox => "0 0 24 24", :width => "24", :xmlns => "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"}
                %line{:x1 => "3", :x2 => "21", :y1 => "12", :y2 => "12"}
                %line{:x1 => "3", :x2 => "21", :y1 => "6", :y2 => "6"}
                %line{:x1 => "3", :x2 => "21", :y1 => "18", :y2 => "18"}
            %nav.ml-auto.header-nav.d-none.d-md-block
              = link_to 'Pricing', pricing_path
              = link_to 'Sign In', login_path


      %main.main
        %section.welcome.welcome-blue.text-white{"aria-label" => "Page header"}
          .container
            .row.align-items-center.justify-content-between
              .col-lg-6.text-center.text-lg-left.pr-lg-5
                %h1.welcome-title Time tracking that matters. Made Simple.
                %p.welcome-description
                  Premium time tracking service for things that matter, to you.
                .mt-5
                  = link_to 'Pricing', pricing_path, class: 'btn btn-green'
                  %a.btn.btn-white.ml-2{:href => "https://preview.tabler.io"} Features
              .col-lg-5.pt-6.pt-lg-0
                .welcome-image.welcome-image-2
                  .device.device-macbook-pro.device-spacegray
                    .device-frame
                      = image_tag 'landing/hourglass_screenshot.png', class: 'preview-image img-responsive'
                    .device-stripe
                    .device-header
                    .device-sensors
                    .device-btns
                    .device-power

        %section.section{"aria-label" => "Base features"}
          .container
            %h2.h3.section-title.text-center.mb-6
              Hourglass comes with tons of
              %br
              well-designed components and features.
            .row.align-items-center.justify-content-center
              .col-10.col-md-5.pr-md-5.mb-5.mb-md-0
                %picture
                  %source{:srcset => "/img/tabler-features.webp", :type => "image/webp"}
                    %source{:srcset => "/img/tabler-features.png", :type => "image/jpeg"}
                      %img.img-responsive{:alt => "", :src => "/img/tabler-features.png"}/
              .col
                .row
                  .col-12.mb-5.d-flex
                    %i.text-muted.mr-2{'data-feather': 'clock', width: 50, height: 50}
                    %div
                      %h3.h5 Record time spent on things that matter
                      %p.text-muted.m-0
                        With Hourglass you can log how many hours in a day you invest in activities that are important to you.
                  .col-12.mb-5.d-flex
                    %i.text-muted.mr-2{'data-feather': 'bar-chart', width: 50, height: 50}
                    %div
                      %h3.h5 Understand your data
                      %p.text-muted.m-0
                        Hourglass provides beautiful components so that you can see how your time data has been logged over the years.
                  .col-12.mb-5.d-flex
                    %i.text-muted.mr-2{'data-feather': 'zap', width: 50, height: 50}
                    %div
                      %h3.h5 Secure your road to mastery.
                      %p.text-muted.m-0
                        Mastering a skill requires a significant investment of hours. Know if you are investing the required hours to achieve your goal!

        %section.section.bg-light
          .container.text-center
            %h2.section-title.mb-2 Ready to start tracking?
            %p.section-description
              Sign up for a free trial. Or see our pricing plans
            .mt-4
              = link_to 'View Pricing', pricing_path, class: 'btn btn-green'

      %footer.footer
        .container
          .row.text-center.text-lg-left
            .col-lg-6
              %p
                Â© 2019 Hourglass
            .col-lg-6.text-lg-right
              %a{:href => "/privacy-policy.html"} Privacy Policy
              %a{:href => "/terms-of-service.html"} Terms of Usage
